@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using Leave_Management.Data

@inject SignInManager<Employee> SignInManager
@inject UserManager<Employee> UserManager

<ul class="navbar-nav">
    @if (SignInManager.IsSignedIn(User))
    {
        <!-- Notifications Dropdown Menu -->
        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">
                <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
            </a>
            <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-lg dropdown-menu-left">

                <span class="dropdown-item dropdown-header">
                    @UserManager.GetUserAsync(User).Result.Firstname @UserManager.GetUserAsync(User).Result.Lastname
                </span>

                <!--Divider-->
                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>

                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Manage/Index" class="dropdown-item">
                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> مشاهده پروفایل
                </a>

                <!--Divider-->
                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>

                <form asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Logout" asp-route-returnUrl="@Url.Action("Index", "Home", new {area = ""})" class="dropdown-item form-inline">
                    <button type="submit" class="dropdown-item" style="cursor: pointer; padding-right: initial;">
                        <i class="fa fa-sign-out" aria-hidden="true"></i> خروج
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" data-widget="control-sidebar" data-slide="true" href="#">
                <i class="fa fa-th-large"></i>
            </a>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item dropdown">
            <a class="nav-link" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">
                <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
            </a>
            <div class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-lg dropdown-menu-left">

                <span class="dropdown-item dropdown-header">ورود / عضویت</span>

                <!--Divider-->
                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>

                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Register" class="dropdown-item">
                    <i class="fa fa-user-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i> ثبت نام
                </a>

                <!--Divider-->
                <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>

                <a asp-area="Identity" asp-page="/Account/Login" class="dropdown-item">
                    <i class="fa fa-sign-in" aria-hidden="true"></i> ورود به سیستم
                </a>

            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" data-widget="control-sidebar" data-slide="true" href="#">
                <i class="fa fa-th-large"></i>
            </a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>
